{"title":"Procurement at MHRA","public_updated_at":"2016-07-18T11:57:09Z","details":{"body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><h2 id=\"doing-business-with-us\">Doing business with us</h2>\n\n<p>Search for agency contract opportunities on <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/contracts-finder\">Contracts Finder</a> . You’ll also find details of contracts worth over £10,000 that we have awarded in the past.</p>\n\n<p>If there’s a Medicines &amp; Healthcare products Regulatory Agency tender you want to take part in, register with our eSourcing system <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://phe.bravosolution.co.uk/web/login.shtml\">Bravo</a>. Please note we are sharing Bravo eSourcing system with Public Health England.</p>\n\n<p>To register on Bravo, you’ll need a <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://europe.dnb.com/find-my-duns/\">DUNS number</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"procurement-contact\">Procurement contact</h2>\n\n<p>If you have a question about agency procurement, email <a href=\"mailto:purchasing@nibsc.org\">purchasing@nibsc.org</a> or telephone 01707 641290.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"standard-terms-and-conditions\">Standard terms and conditions</h2>\n\n<p><span id=\"attachment_1633330\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n  <a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/538154/TCs_for_the_Provision_of_Goods.pdf\">Terms and Conditions for the Provision of Goods</a>\n  (<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">174KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">12 pages</span>)\n</span></p>\n\n<p><span id=\"attachment_1635596\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n  <a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/538156/TCs_for_the_Provision_of_Services.pdf\">Terms and Conditions for the Provision of services</a>\n  (<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">179KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">13 pages</span>)\n</span></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"procurement-for-small-and-medium-sized-enterprises\">Procurement for small and medium-sized enterprises</h2>\n\n<p>See our <span id=\"attachment_1633370\" class=\"attachment-inline\">\n  <a href=\"/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/538276/SME_Policy.pdf\">Small and Medium-sized Enterprise (SME) Action Plan </a>\n  (<span class=\"type\"><abbr title=\"Portable Document Format\">PDF</abbr></span>, <span class=\"file-size\">108KB</span>, <span class=\"page-length\">1 page</span>)\n</span></p>\n\n</div>","organisation":"240f72bd-9a4d-4f39-94d9-77235cadde8e","tags":{"browse_pages":[],"policies":[],"topics":[]}},"routes":[{"path":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency/about/procurement","type":"exact"}],"redirects":[],"publishing_app":"whitehall","rendering_app":"government-frontend","need_ids":[],"phase":"live","analytics_identifier":null,"document_type":"procurement","schema_name":"corporate_information_page","first_published_at":"2016-07-18T11:57:13Z","base_path":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency/about/procurement","description":"","content_id":"2d1cb367-9da3-4b17-900a-0b1fa4572bd1","locale":"en","expanded_links":{"organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"EA63","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency","base_path":"/government/organisations/medicines-and-healthcare-products-regulatory-agency","content_id":"240f72bd-9a4d-4f39-94d9-77235cadde8e","description":null,"document_type":"organisation","locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2015-06-29T14:33:29Z","schema_name":"placeholder","title":"Medicines and Healthcare products Regulatory Agency","withdrawn":false,"details":{"brand":"department-of-health","logo":{"formatted_title":"Medicines &amp; Healthcare products<br/>Regulatory Agency","crest":"single-identity"}},"links":{}}],"available_translations":[{"title":"Procurement at MHRA","public_updated_at":"2016-07-18T11:57:09Z","analytic